text: Catriel Ignacio Sánchez (born 17 July 1998) is an Argentine professional footballer who plays as a striker for Talleres de Córdoba. ==Career== Sánchez is a product of Talleres de Córdoba youth sportive system and made his debut for this club in the Argentine Primera División on June 2017. In February 2018, was announced that he was close for signing of a contract with the Ukrainian Premier League club FC Karpaty Lviv.
